  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims at enabling women, children and men affected by leprosy and other neglected diseases to transform their lives by overcoming poverty, stigma and discrimination. Purpose or specific objectives: 1. To promote early and increased case detection for leprosy among women and children. 2. To prevent disability and to halt the worsening of existing disability among people affected by leprosy. 3. To empower people affected by leprosy and their forums to claim their rights and entitlements.</narrative>
  </description>
